{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_9","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc 'cat .harness/notes.md'","aggregated_output":"# MiniLang Harness Notes (2026-06-07)\n\n- Verified `RULES.md` behavior against visible tests in `test/lsp.visible.test.mjs`.\n- Implemented transport framing, lifecycle, diagnostics publish, completion, definition, and hover entirely in `src/server.mjs`.\n- Ran `npm test` repeatedly until full visible pass:\n- JSON-RPC transport: pass\n- initialize/shutdown/exit: pass\n- didOpen diagnostics + stale-clear behavior on didChange: pass\n- completion: pass\n- definition/hover: pass\n- No remaining visible gaps.\n- QA-Reviewer pass (current run):\n- `npm test` results: 5 passed, 0 failed.\n- Manual check 1/3: `MessageBuffer.push` correctly decodes chunked payloads and preserves message order across split writes.\n- Manual check 2/3: `textDocument/didOpen` then `textDocument/didChange` on same URI updates document state and publishes refreshed diagnostics (including stale-clear behavior).\n- Manual check 3/3: `initialize` capabilities include expected providers; `shutdown`/`exit` follow LSP expectation (`exit` -> 0 only after shutdown, otherwise 1).\n- No code changes required in `src/server.mjs`; no actionable failures recorded.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
